title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12V AIR COMPRESSOR PX01 WIRING KIT

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12V AIR COMPRESSOR PX01 WIRING KIT

Boss Air 12V Air Compressor PX01 Wiring Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744!

Contains:

  • 6m Power Cable
  • Waterproof Fuse Holder
  • 15 amp Fuse
  • Terminals for connecting Boss Air’s PX01 compressor from Battery/switch to red positive terminal

To view the full range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
